	dprr:hasNoteText "Named on a milestone near Gabii with Caecilius Q. f. (CIL 1(2) 2.833). The letters CVR appear on the stone, which may be dated to the third or early second century. A curule aedile or curator of uncertain date. (RS, CP)\n" .
